quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,94,Futhi asizange sithumele umphrofethi edolobheni ngaphandle kokuthi sabamba abantu balo (idolobha) ngenhlupheko nobunzima mhlawumbe ukuze bazithobe
  7,95,"Sabe sesishintsha esikhundleni sokubi ngokuhle kwaze kwaba bayanda futhi bathi, “obaba bethu bathintwa ubunzima nenjabulo ngakho-ke sabathatha ngokuzamayo ngesikhathi benganakile"
  7,96,Futhi uma abantu bamadolobha babekholiwe futhi benza ubuqotho ngempela sasizobavulela izibusiso ezivela ezulwini nasemhlabeni kepha banqaba ngakho-ke sabathatha ngenxa yalokho ababekuzuza (ababekwenza)
  7,97,Kungabe bazizwa bephephile yini abantu basemadolobheni maqondana nokuthi kuze kubona isijeziso sethu ebusuku ngesikhathi bona belele na
  7,98,Noma ngakube bazizwa bephephile yini abantu basemadolobheni maqondana nokuthi kuze kubona isijeziso sethu ekuseni ngesikhathi bona bedlala na
  7,99,"Ngakube bazizwa bephephile ecebweni likaMvelinqangi, kepha akukho namunye ophephile ecebweni likaMvelinqangi ngaphandle kwabantu abalahlekelweyo"